pageContext.claim: “And we're bringing back [MS-13] to where they came from.”
pageContext.analysis: Although MS-13 is now run out of El Salvador, the gang originated in Los Angeles in the 1980s. In other words, not all members of MS-13 can be returned "to where they came from" because they are American. In 2017, the Justice Department estimated there were about 10,000 total active members in the United States and 30,000 around the world.
